## Summary
This documentation details the CleverTap Event Stream integration with Amplitude, allowing event data to be ingested from Amplitude into CleverTap for engagement purposes. It covers setup requirements including CleverTap credentials (Account ID, Passcode, Region), configuration steps in both platforms, and explains how the integration enables advanced analytics, personalized campaigns, and customer retention strategies.

